com.blockwithme.util.shared

Class MurmurHash

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.blockwithme.util.shared.MurmurHash

  • public final class MurmurHash
extends Object
    File copied from http://d3s.mff.cuni.cz/~holub/sw/javamurmurhash/MurmurHash.java Murmur hash 2.0. The murmur hash is a relative fast hash function from http://murmurhash.googlepages.com/ for platforms with efficient multiplication. This is a re-implementation of the original C code plus some additional features. Public domain.
    Version:
    1.0.2 TODO Test if this works in GWT (gives same results as in Java).
    Author:
    Viliam Holub
